{"id": "1429340714457632958", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "总之扔一下，你游考据迄今为止最大未解之谜：克珀的背景文字来源\n由于实在找不到完全一致的描述，姑且认为这段话大概率是你游文案原创\n但是它和其他同期疑似文案原创的背景文字（克莱/杜勒）遣词造句风格完全不同，其中提到的沼泽/蒸汽/女巫般的诡异火焰等元素也几乎无法贴合克珀的角色故事，而克莱杜勒的内容基本是按照角色塑造来的\n无论如何其行文风格都和直接搬原著的鸟鸟/朵尔皮的背景文字更为相像…可偏偏所有能找到的，原著里出现的圣艾尔摩之火的提及全都是一笔带过的比喻…\n我投降了，你游文案时隔一年终于再次制造出了惊喜而不是惊吓~~又或许只是又一次文案间相互打架的例证而已？~~\n砖头抛这儿了，期待解答", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T05:29:42.193000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429340823190896752", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://docs.google.com/document/u/0/d/10KUHLOwLHEp33bjzUiJpLo_zQ5Q8Z9ITf_vlHxTJAYE/mobilebasic\n顺带放一下隔壁英区整理的背景文字合集", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T05:30:08.117000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "link", "title": "[Morimens Hidden English Texts]", "url": "https://docs.google.com/document/u/0/d/10KUHLOwLHEp33bjzUiJpLo_zQ5Q8Z9ITf_vlHxTJAYE/mobilebasic", "description": "Chaos  Ramona: “All that was, and is, and is to be, exists simultaneously.”  Ramona - Timeworn: All that was, and is, and is to be, exists simultaneously.”  Doll: “Mind and body of living organisms.” “Great God! That whisperer in darkness with its morbid odours and vibrations! Sorcerer, emissary,..."}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429383625513631805", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我有個陰間想法👁️", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T08:20:12.986000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1301813973703852035"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429340714457632958", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429389004297601064", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "但還是先從最普通的字面翻譯來說個人解讀好了\n先說我的克系知識儲備絕對不會比讀過原著的各位大佬精通，所以以下都是身為業餘創作者試圖去揣摩文案寫作思路的，個人觀點方面的推測和解讀啊😅要罵我請小力一點😭", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T08:41:35.388000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429389304039477391", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "首先啊貼上一般字體的原文比較好閱讀\n\nThe swamp exhaled vapours that shimmered with a pallid luminescence, akin to witch-fire or that eldritch glow named for St. Elmo’s—yet here it writhed as if alive.", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T08:42:46.852000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429391224661475329", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "既然是克珀的背景文字，那這一定是在描寫克珀相關的東西嘛。\n要寫描寫時思路不外乎兩個路線：一是這個角色（也許是除了艾爾摩以外的原型，也許是本人），二就是聖艾爾摩之火本火\n從後面有出現聖艾爾摩之火來作為譬喻的話，那先暫定這段文字是在描寫角色的吧。", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T08:50:24.764000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:43:02.857000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429392815032369152", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "那先撇掉比較有疑問的swamp (沼澤）和 vapor （蒸氣）第一句不看。\n\n“akin to witch-fire or that eldritch glow named for St. Elmo’s”\n翻譯過來就是「類似於 witch-fire 或是那以聖艾爾摩命名的奇特光芒」", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T08:56:43.938000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429393943681957928", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "文學感是一個很微妙的東西啊，說白點就是大量的譬喻法。\n而且英文裡這種名詞-名詞的寫法本身就帶有一種「具有名詞1性質的名詞2」，再加上他跟聖艾爾摩一起被拿來類比，所以在這裡的witch-fire，個人想法是不應該被字面翻譯成「女巫之火」，而應該被翻譯成「妖火」或是「巫火」", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:01:13.029000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:02:11.070000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429394969885540464", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "只有同性質的東西才會被拿來類比，那跟聖艾爾摩之火同性質、又像是火焰的自然詭異現象是什麼呢？\n沒錯就是鬼火 AKA “will-‘o-the-wisp”", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:05:17.695000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:06:05.199000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429395730673438781", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "但“will-‘o-the-wisp”寫在句子裡太長了破壞閱讀感，寫個ghost fire 感覺又太通俗（\n所以推測這邊使用了witch-fire 是這個原因（當然也可能是翻譯機的鍋我不能確定）", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:08:19.081000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429396653663850588", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "得出第二句營造的氛圍了啊，那現在可以回頭拆解比較迷惑的第一句。\n\n但再次聲明因為我不是文案，所以我絕對不知道這句被寫出來時創作者到底想寫的是什麼😂，只能從目前結果來推測可能的意思，完全就是先射箭再畫靶。", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:11:59.139000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429398127999324355", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "——“The swamp exhaled vapours that shimmered with a pallid luminescence”\n\n「那沼澤（swamp)散發出閃耀著蒼白光芒的蒸氣（vapor)」", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:17:50.648000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429400174714687568", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為還不確定具體意思所以先這樣字面翻譯。\n剛也說了，有時候文學感的寫作就是大量的比喻，但抽象代指也是一種手法。\n就有點像中文裡的月亮可能會被用銅鏡來代指這樣。\n\n那這樣很難懂的這句也許就有兩個解讀方向：\n1. 沼澤和蒸氣就是字面上的意思\n2. 沼澤和蒸氣是代指", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:25:58.623000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429401289544175707", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "先從代指下手吧，因為只要猜代指的那個東西就好了嘛。\n那考慮到克珀的海洋背景，「沼澤」跟「蒸氣」最直接的一個猜測就是「海洋」和「海面的霧氣（或者某種煙霧）」\n但既然使用代指就代表這兩個東西有相同性質，或者說至少要讓讀者能在腦中聯想。", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:30:24.419000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429402099057164439", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以加入沼澤特性，這邊用swamp可能是在代指某種「像沼澤一樣的淺水/物體」", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:33:37.422000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:45:59.526000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429403002921553990", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果是指什麼物體的話，那就蠻符合我們前面推測說這文本是在描寫角色本人甚至包含可能的隱藏原型\n但這句其實不管怎麼翻譯都蠻難懂的😅，再細分的話就是這個「像沼澤一樣的物體難道又是在隱喻什麼嗎？！」有點可能性太多了", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:37:12.920000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429403288566104144", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "大概就這樣\n我說完了（高歌離席", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:38:21.023000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429404448882556968", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "我看網路上的資料，卡索格薩的設定有蒸氣的描述，也有帶電的雲氣；所以原本我在猜是不是跟她有關聯（而且好像也有跟克總打過架", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:42:57.664000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😮", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429403002921553990", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429404477076668416", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:43:04.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1429404476497985536", "filename": "Screenshot_20251019-174236475.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 209114, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1429404476497985536/Screenshot_20251019-174236475.jpg?ex=6a35b7e8&is=6a346668&hm=a765532c561567def2e80caf61b59e4a1094ddc8e51695577ff4feed910f6fdc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429404549344395377", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是克柏立繪整體好像比較偏向純粹的雷電，所以我覺得她可能還有喇另一個弗塔古亞", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:43:21.616000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429404747957407754", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "炎之精這樣🤔🤔🤔", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:44:08.969000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429407118661779496", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "是这样，看到这个文字，咱第一眼感觉是原著摘录的原因是（1）这个witch-fire相当像英文小说常用的名词衔接表达（2）较长的文学化的句子和相当具有克苏鲁标志的用词（pallid luminescence/eldritch glow）\n确实是很微妙的东西…结果便是，「沼泽」这种偏阴暗潮湿的意象，连同witch/eldritch这种引发（偏负面的，险恶的）神秘相关联想的选词，得到了一个相对朦胧阴郁的氛围\n而这个氛围是与克珀角色故事里她坚定的，昂扬的，甚至可以说是一根筋的精神不搭的，如果要描述一个行为如此明晰的人物，没有必要使用前半段那样长串的暗示性隐喻\n嗯就是很矛盾（", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:53:34.189000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:53:46.284000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429393943681957928", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429407419519209606", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "神仙對話", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:54:45.919000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429407498603069440", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "👀 🍿", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:55:04.774000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍿", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429407548397719653", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "確實，但我認為拿來迎合整個克蘇魯神話的歌德陰溼風的話，這樣整體氛圍感確實是沒啥問題的", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:55:16.646000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429408464949477477", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以才說這段文字可能是講克珀也可能是講她的不知名原型，而這陰鬱的氛圍是屬於那個原型的", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T09:58:55.169000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429408804625453117", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "这个是摇同担过来一通搜索之后得到的最接近结果…后一个作品没看过（缩）前一个作品是史密斯的，整体也是那种阴郁幽暗的调调\n有一种可能是文案从史密斯这篇中借用了「黑暗中的火光」的形象，又把phosphorescent radiance改成了更为具体的圣艾尔摩之火，重新塑造出了克珀的形象", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:00:16.154000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1429408804377853972", "filename": "9A31B993-056B-4529-9EB3-6430A9A1304A.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 252829, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1429408804377853972/9A31B993-056B-4529-9EB3-6430A9A1304A.png?ex=6a35bbf0&is=6a346a70&hm=101636669f6f5c8151a9477da638526d9816749020dedd165e41a011978931cd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429408888431710301", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "贴一下原文（\nhttp://www.eldritchdark.com/writings/short-stories/114/the-light-from-the-pole", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:00:36.135000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429409253264855167", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "是說雖然我還沒打到星辰篇（\n但是星辰篇的調調是不是整體看起來有點二元抗爭的感覺🤔\n像是n對抗地瓜，雙子反抗尋求自由\n所以我在想克柏是不是也有類似的概念？以行星指引反抗大海的風暴帶船隻前行的部分，會不會也是因為這樣所以她的設定會很矛盾（很像克蘇魯家族系列但又是正向理智的性格", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:02:03.118000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
