{"id": "1429409940975386700", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "599171149431046156", "author_name": "foxcatfurry", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~預告?是說他接受海國提案要帶各位(?)去海國啦~~", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:04:47.081000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429410157279842406", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "根據氛圍，這文案更超譯誇張一點的翻譯甚至能翻成「那如沼澤般的爛泥正散發著閃耀蒼白光芒的煙霧。好似鬼火，又或是那以聖艾爾摩命名的奇特光芒——但它卻痛苦的扭動著，像是擁有生命般。」", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:05:38.652000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:05:46.754000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429408464949477477", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429410429360410715", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以我的陰間暴論就是，有沒有可能這是被雷劈之後正在垂死掙扎的克珊😄（不要啊", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:06:43.521000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429410521379115094", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "開玩笑的但超譯才是文學閱讀的精髓（乾", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:07:05.460000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429410762887270410", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且她的劇情敘述有提到其實體內的雷電對她而言是痛苦的懲罰，所以我腦洞結果是她雖然有卡索格薩的元素，但是她在反抗風暴循著繁星指引的最後一刻吸引到了炎之精弗塔古亞（跟星星有關、藍色雷電、自燃），但個人劇情來看最後還是~~帶大家去海國辣~~\n以上個人腦洞🤡☝️", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:08:03.040000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429410922618818590", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769869355193204737", "author_name": "tsubaki9884", "author_bot": false, "content": "佬們腦洞真好看<:pray:1356053116260454534>", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:08:41.123000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429411287489839144", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~弗塔古亞的設定好像少的很可憐🌿~~", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:10:08.115000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1429411287137255495", "filename": "Screenshot_20251019-180924297.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 229473, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1429411287137255495/Screenshot_20251019-180924297.jpg?ex=6a35be40&is=6a346cc0&hm=7c2e4293e91517fcff42c1d71ac09ab4b192727d11d202b2e2495fbf1e87e046&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429412035539632291", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過凱蒂已經是克圖了，而且看劇情她身邊也圍繞著炎之精（嗎？她那些死掉的隊友是不是變炎精了）那這樣感覺克珀還混炎精就有點不搭了", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:13:06.464000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429412503263383613", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "對ㄉ，但弗塔古亞是炎精裡比較特別（藍藍ㄉ）一位，而且其實克圖的炎精跟弗塔古亞跟是來自不同著作🌿", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:14:57.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429412035539632291", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429412739226534013", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "最後還有一本著作試圖把他們喇在一起通稱炎精，所以不知道遊戲是走分開還是統一的部分(⁠´⁠ ⁠.⁠ ⁠.̫⁠ ⁠.⁠ ⁠`⁠)", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:15:54.236000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429412991841075301", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "欸这么说突然想到，克珀故事里她固执的坚持和一根筋，或许有可能本身就是被深海的疯狂影响的结果？对其他更世俗的人类是激发他们的恐惧，对克珀就是把她的坚定放大成偏执什么的…\n这样把克珀的剧情理解成一个被疯狂和极端情绪支配的故事的话…有可能这段话反而是说的从更接近现实的角度看，克珀那起船难的描述呢（）沼泽其实是船最终强行登岸的地方，烟雾来源是雷劈之后的灰烬什么的", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:16:54.464000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429414001141616700", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "這也是一種合理的可能，所以才說除非寫的人親自出來公布正確答案，不然文學的閱讀理解其實都是非常自由且分歧的（所以有時候才覺得對於作品想表達什麼的爭吵真的是很沒必要", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:20:55.100000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:04:39.657000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1301813973703852035"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429412991841075301", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429415460780113981", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "補充網路上查到很有趣的部分是想把這兩個喇在一起的著作是⟨The Horror in the Gallery⟩\n這部是在講一個阻止深潛者用小雕像召喚舊日支配者Zoth-Ommog的故事，最後他們是丟某個神奇星形石頭釋放出閃電能量把怪物劈死ㄉ（大概？", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:26:43.105000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429412739226534013", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429419671265869845", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "🌿克柏有沒有可能是那顆石頭（舊印）有關？用來封印跟保護用的", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:43:26.963000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429415460780113981", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
