{"id": "1429420177921015828", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "乾她大招炸下來不就是那個眼睛的樣子嗎🌿", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T10:45:27.759000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429435561604546720", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "舊印是戰爭女神的標誌，之所以其他神話生物怕這個其實是怕它背後的主人", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T11:46:35.515000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429435610539491358", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "但戰爭女神的資料少的可憐", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T11:46:47.182000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "4️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429439680486703175", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "769245092351180871", "author_name": "ass191044", "author_bot": false, "content": "我今天才知道原來外神跟舊日支配者之外還有古神🌿", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:02:57.533000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["422799061133950978"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429435610539491358", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429441825042726922", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得這十分有可能，因為 phosphorescent radiance 字面翻譯就是「散發磷光的光芒」\n這樣就跟克珀劇情內《領航員輓歌》內提到的化為磷光對上了。而且順帶一提，鬼火的另一個名稱就是磷火", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:11:28.835000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:26:19.820000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1301813973703852035"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1429408804625453117", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429442381425414155", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "但鬼火的元素實在是太不好做題了，沒搞好可能就會像普通的火。啊然後正好又有個跟海洋和船強相關的聖艾爾摩之火😂所以克珀最終變成電漿女了😂", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:13:41.487000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:14:12.111000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1429443226430996540", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "啊再順帶一提一個沒用小知識\n字首phos就是磷的意思，所以你看到phos啥啥啥的，中文有很大概率就是和磷有關的東西", "timestamp": "2025-10-19T12:17:02.952000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
